task.summary: Default task
Added script to scrub non-english characters from training data.
Modified data loading so that the only text processing done at runtime is adding START and END characters. All other text preprocessing is done ahead of time.
Modified data loading so that the only text processing done at runtime is adding START and END characters. All other text preprocessing is done ahead of time.
Modified data loading so that the only text processing done at runtime is adding START and END characters. All other text preprocessing is done ahead of time.

Added gan_embedding argument to specify when the user would like to use the GAN's embeddings instead of those given by a pretrained ResNet. Also added functionality/argument to resume from most alphabetically recent checkpoint file.
Added START and END characters to vocab at initialization.

Basic (successful) attempt to get beam search decoding working. Created an entirely new DecoderRNNOld.decode() function that decodes one character at a time, allowing for beam search.
Code should be cleaned up. Beam search should be improved.
Added code to save images while training.
Changed prune candidates to select top k, instead of sorting.
Remove old comments.
Change default caption printing, caption print length, and checkpoint naming convention.
Fix whitespace, saving string formatting.
Refactor main function to reduce size and enable easier swapping out of different encoders/decoders.
For caption only dataset, splits captions into "ABCD" -> "AB" + "CD" instead of "AB" + "BC" +"CD". Made seq len optional argument.
Added simple write to logfile.
Separated hidden state sizes.
Fixed beam_search_decode to first give decoder the encoded image/caption from the encoder. Then, it gives the decoder a starting character.
Added argument for num_layers in EncoderRNN.
Alter beam_search_decode to add noise to decoding. Implement multinomial sampling based caption generation in generate_text.
Add argument to enable beam search if desired. Defaults to using multinomial decoding sampling.
Delete unused code.
Remove extraneous default value.
Remove extraneous default value.
Add in-depth support for logging (log file, arguments, print statements, images, etc.) resume argument must now include name of model to resume training from. generate_text now returns log prob.
Fix temp write out.
